---
title: Indonesian-Style Stir-Fried Noodles and Shrimp with Fried Eggs and Crispy Shallots
description: These stir-fried noodles are inspired by the popular Indonesian dish 'mie goreng.' A sweet, savoury sauce coats fresh chow mein noodles and vibrant veggies, and shrimp, crispy shallots and a fried egg make every bite super satisfying!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-sautees-et-crevettes-a-lindonesienne-cef380c5.jpg
